0:{"buildId":"I3GEKSVLVTWqxcEXDRaWq","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 22301 Self-assessment Checklist"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:31:03+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"ISO 22301 Self-assessment checklist helps the organization to verify that your ISO 22301 system is perfect for the organizations in  Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah,"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22301 Self-assessment Checklist"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To ensure consistency and completeness, WIZMS designed an ISO 22301 self assessment checklist. ISO 22301 self assessment checklist helps the organization to verify that your ISO 22301 system has each of the following elements associated with Sections 5-10 of ISO 22301 standard. It can also be used as an ISO 22301 audit checklist, if your organization in UAE is preparing to undergo an official ISO 22301 certification process."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Business recovery plan is an essential plan to meet ISO 22301 business continuity standards Find out the important elements of a successful plan and get sample checklists in this free guide."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22301 self assessment Checklist"}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 5 : Leadership Requirements"}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To get ISO 22301 certification in Dubai, it is necessary to have an management committee, along with a process that dictates how the committee will manage the system from the time of creation, implementation, and maintenance. Organization’s policies and objectives align with the requirements of ISO 22301. If you have more intense legal/regulatory, customer and stakeholder requirements, then your policies must match your obligations."}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 6: ISO 22301 Audit Checklist Planning Requirements"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Adequate planning is required to get ISO 22301 certification. Organization should identify the risks involved while implementing the BCMS ISO 22301 standard. The company should set clear cut policies, objectives, and criteria to measure its success."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 7: Support Requirements"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To support the BCMS ISO 22301 Certification, employees should have knowledge, skills and experience to develop and maintain the system properly. All the employees should be aware of their roles, responsibilities and business continuity management issues."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 8 : Operations Requirements"}],"$L2","$L3","$L4","$L5","$L6","$L7","$L8"]}],"$L9"]}]}],["$La"],"$Lb"]}],"loading":null,"isPartial":false}
2:["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The organization in UAE must understand how disruptions might affect operations of ISO 22301. A risk assessment will reveal the threats that your business faces. Based on that BCMS will be implemented effectively. Clause 8 favors short, quick understanding of business continuity plans. These documents will provide a fast response. It's usually better to create a strategy for each potential plan than one large plan for all the potential events. The last section addresses exercises and tests. Interruptions may occur at any time, checking those responses will work when need is crucial. Testing the ISO 22301 system determines whether one element of the business continuity arrangements passes or fails."}]
3:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 9: Evaluation Requirements"}]
4:["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The next ISO 22301 checklist is to evaluate the performance of an organization. Using some of the established metrics, an organization can measure its performance over time. Based on the ISO 22301 internal audit checklist, the organization must conduct ISO 22301 audits."}]
5:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Clause 10 — Improvement"}]
6:["$","p","15",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Going hand-in-hand with evaluation, the organization must improve the system. ISO 22301Certification in UAE recognizes that all the arrangement must be perfect from the start which requires improvement as part of the ISO 22301 certification. Therefore, the organization must take corrective actions based on the results of ISO 22301 internal audits, reviews and exercises."}]
7:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO Certification in UAE is a most preferred Certification Standard by organizations in UAE from all sectors. Wizms provides ISO Certificate in UAE for all major standards such as ISO 9001:2015, ISO 14001:2015, ISO 27001:2015, ISO 17025:2017, ISO 45001:2018 and more."}]
8:["$","p","17",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms is the best ISO consultant in UAE and provides ISO consulting services in Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ras al-Khaimah, Ajman, Al Ain and Fujairah. Wizms ISO consultant in Dubai offers top-class ISO consultancy services including ISO Consulting, ISO Certification, ISO Training in UAE, Gap analysis, Documentation, Implementation, and ISO certification audits in UAE."}]
